*Robu* je pospremio u sobu. (He put the goods in the room.)

*Robu* je naručio preko interneta. (He ordered the goods online.)

*Robu* je trebalo da isporuči u roku. (The goods had to be delivered on time.)

*Roba* je bila spremna za promet. (The goods were ready for sale.)

*Robu* je trebalo da kupi. (He had to buy the goods.)

*Robom* je trgovalo već dugo. (They have been trading goods for a long time.)

*Robu* je trebalo da isporuči preko noći. (The goods had to be delivered overnight.)

*Robu* je trebalo da proda. (He had to sell the goods.)